import {Container, Grid} from '@mui/material';
import {Box} from '@mui/system';

const Header = () => {
   return (

                  R

                  A
               </Box>
               <Box component="div" sx={{display: 'inline'}}>
                  I
               </Box>
               <Box component="div" sx={{display: 'inline'}}>
                  N
               </Box>
               <Box component="div" sx={{display: 'inline'}}>
                  B
               </Box>
               <Box component="div" sx={{display: 'inline'}}>
                  O
               </Box>
               <Box component="div" sx={{display: 'inline'}}>
                  W
               </Box>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
               <Link>About the app</Link>
            </Grid>
         </Grid>
      </Container>
   );
};

export default Header;
